"Jake\n\nIntroduction:\n\nI had the pleasure of meeting Jake Bonner on the day of his graduation shoot. He's a very bright young man graduating from Bowie High School in Maryland this May. He plans to attend Bowie University just miles away while majoring in Computer Science. During his time in high school, Jake played football as both a running back and linebacker. It's safe to say that he all-around liked to impose his will on the field! His mother is extremely proud of him as he's her first and only son. She contacted me for the shoot and told me all about how it was raising him--moving from Mississippi just to make sure he had as many opportunities as possible. Jake certainly has all the potential in the world to be great and we wish him well as he takes the next step in his life. Congratulations!"
